{
  "version": 1,
  "course": {
    "id": "nce1-081-082-roast-beef-and-potatoes",
    "title": "Lesson 81: Roast beef and potatoes",
    "audioFilename": "081&082－Roast Beef and Potatoes.mp3",
    "duration": 84.558,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.24,
      "end": 5.46,
      "text": "Lesson 81–Roast Beef and Potatoes.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第81课——烤牛肉和土豆。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 7.14,
      "end": 11.08,
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 12.52,
      "end": 14.84,
      "text": "Why is Carol disappointed?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "卡罗尔为什么感到失望？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 16.98,
      "end": 17.92,
      "text": "Hi, Carol.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你好，卡罗尔。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 18.74,
      "end": 19.56,
      "text": "Where's Tom?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "汤姆在哪里？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 20.26,
      "end": 21.6,
      "text": "He's upstairs.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他在楼上。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 22.48,
      "end": 23.98,
      "text": "He's having a bath.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他正在洗澡。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 25.18,
      "end": 25.82,
      "text": "Tom?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "汤姆？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 26.6,
      "end": 27.32,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "什么事？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 28.46,
      "end": 29.02,
      "text": "Sam's here.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "萨姆来了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 29.02,
      "end": 31.5,
      "text": "I'm nearly ready.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我马上就好。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 32.78,
      "end": 33.76,
      "text": "Hello, Sam.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你好，萨姆。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 34.72,
      "end": 35.72,
      "text": "Have a cigarette.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "来支香烟吧。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 36.56,
      "end": 38.1,
      "text": "No, thanks, Tom.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "不了，谢谢，汤姆。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 39.2,
      "end": 41.16,
      "text": "Have a glass of whiskey, then.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "那就喝杯威士忌吧。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "start": 41.68,
      "end": 43.04,
      "text": "Okay, thanks.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "好的，谢谢。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "start": 44.24,
      "end": 49.36,
      "text": "Is dinner ready? It's nearly ready.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "晚饭好了吗？快好了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "start": 50.1,
      "end": 53.14,
      "text": "We can have dinner at seven o'clock.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我们七点钟可以吃晚饭。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "start": 54.84,
      "end": 57.76,
      "text": "Sam and I had lunch together today.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "萨姆和我今天一起吃了午饭。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "start": 57.76,
      "end": 60.28,
      "text": "We went to a restaurant.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我们去了一家餐馆。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "start": 61.14,
      "end": 62.5,
      "text": "What did you have?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你们吃了什么？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "start": 63.54,
      "end": 66.22,
      "text": "We had roast beef and potatoes.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我们吃了烤牛肉和土豆。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s023",
      "start": 67.12,
      "end": 67.54,
      "text": "Oh!",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "哦！"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s024",
      "start": 68.5,
      "end": 70.14,
      "text": "What's the matter, Carol?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "怎么了，卡罗尔？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s025",
      "start": 71.18,
      "end": 77.22,
      "text": "Well, you're going to have roast beef and potatoes again tonight.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "嗯，今晚你们又要吃烤牛肉和土豆了。"
      }
    }
  ]
}
